# rather than the shared tagless one. --category accepts one or more cat###
# (comma-separated); each must exist on disk (same dangling-link guard as
# adr). Body comes from stdin (the brainstormer composes `## problem`); CLI
# handles id allocation, frontmatter (+ session id), the `# Spec [[cat###]]...
